--And Zvarri...

502
00:21:10,250 --> 00:21:13,250
This testimony will
take its toll on you.

503
00:21:13,333 --> 00:21:16,375
You miserable minion
of Mask DeMasque.

504
00:21:16,458 --> 00:21:18,125
[sighs]
Minion, eh?

505
00:21:18,208 --> 00:21:22,958
[LUKE chuckles] Although,
I alone am not your adversary.

506
00:21:23,041 --> 00:21:25,416
Tomorrow's trial will
introduce a terrible threat

507
00:21:25,500 --> 00:21:28,041
who will truly thwart
your thriving trajectory.

508
00:21:28,125 --> 00:21:29,541
What do you mean?

509
00:21:29,625 --> 00:21:31,583
[LUKE] A defense's most
fearsome foe is a properly

510
00:21:31,666 --> 00:21:33,958
