511
00:21:34,041 --> 00:21:35,833
You may be used to
Edgeworth's excellence,

512
00:21:35,916 --> 00:21:38,291
but your next enemy
is without equal.

513
00:21:38,375 --> 00:21:40,291
He is correctly called the
most cunning counselor

514
00:21:40,375 --> 00:21:43,500
in the country.
But you may know him as...

515
00:21:43,583 --> 00:21:45,041
...Godot!

516
00:21:45,125 --> 00:21:49,708
[GODOT] Hmph. We're to do battle
in this gladiator's arena.

517
00:21:49,791 --> 00:21:50,875
[PHOENIX gasps]

518
00:21:50,958 --> 00:21:52,208
The sole reason

519
00:21:52,291 --> 00:21:54,875
I've returned from
the ghastly depths of Hell.

