523
00:23:35,000 --> 00:23:36,541
Standing before
me is the resurrected,

524
00:23:36,625 --> 00:23:39,666
undefeated, legendary
prosecutor, Godot!

525
00:23:39,750 --> 00:23:41,583
Something stinks
about this case.

526
